)ATTR DEFAULT(%+_)
)BODY
%TUTORIAL ---------------  MANUAL MANAGEMENT FACILITY  ----------------
%SELECTION ===>_ZCMD
%
%                              ------------------
                               ×     UPDATE     ×
                               ------------------
+
   The%UPDATE+command allows authorised users to update information for
   manuals on the LEB's Manual data base.

   The first panel allows the user to update the following fields:

   CURRENCY                1 character
   PRODUCT NUMBER          8 characters in the format XXXX-XXX, required
   NUMBER OF COPIES        1-50, required, may not be decreased
   TNL LEVEL               9 characters in the format XXXX-XXXX
   VERSION                 6 characters
   DESCRIPTION             70 characters, required


                            (continued on next page)
)PROC
   &ZCONT = LMMPH130
   &ZUP = LMMPH010
)END
